-> ''The term “textile sourcing” refers to the process of finding, selecting, and obtaining fabrics or raw textile materials that will later be used to make clothing. So, if “apparel production” is the stage where garments are actually manufactured, “textile sourcing” is the stage where the materials for those garments are secured and prepared.''

